pe":"text","value":" 和数列 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"B=\\lbrace b_1,b_2,\\cdots,b_N \\rbrace"},{"type":"text","value":"，若 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"C=\\lbrace c_1,c_2,\\cdots,c_K \\rbrace"},{"type":"text","value":" 既是 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"A"},{"type":"text","value":" 的子序列，又是 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"B"},{"type":"text","value":" 的子序列，则称 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"C"},{"type":"text","value":" 是 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"A"},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"B"},{"type":"text","value":" 的公共子序列。"},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"A"},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"B"},{"type":"text","value":" 的最长公共子序列指 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"A"},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"B"},{"type":"text","value":" 的所有公共子序列中元素个数最多的那些。"}]},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"算法一"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"记 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"dp(i,j)"},{"type":"text","value":" 表示 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"\\lbrace a_1, a_2, \\cdots, a_i \\rbrace"},{"type":"text","value":" 和\n"},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"\\lbrace b_1, b_2, \\cdots, b_j \\rbrace"},{"type":"text","value":" 的最长上升子序列长度，不难发现转移方程为："}]},{"type":"math","value":"dp(i,j) = dp(i-1, j-1) + f(i, j), \\quad\\text{其中}\\; f(i,j) = \\left\\lbrace\\begin{aligned}&0, &i \\geqslant M \\;\\text{或}\\;  j \\geqslant N \\;\\text{或}\\; a_i \\neq a_j\\\\&1, &i < M \\;\\text{且}\\;  j < N \\;\\text{且}\\; a_i=a_j \\end{aligned}\\right."}]},"fields":{"slug":"/quiz/algorithm/LCS/"}}]},"postItems":{"nodes":[{"title":"最长公共子序列（LCS）","createAt":"2021-06-02","tags":["quiz","最长公共子序列","LCS"],"fields":{"slug":"/quiz/algorithm/LCS/"}},{"title":"最长上升子序列（LIS）","createAt":"2021-06-02","tags":["quiz","最长上升子序列","LIS"],"fields":{"slug":"/quiz/algorithm/LIS/"}},{"title":"不修改数组找出重复的数字","createAt":"2021-06-29","tags":["quiz","分治","追击"],"fields":{"slug":"/quiz/algorithm/partition/